movies.description: Scooby-Doo and Shaggy must go into the underworld ruled by the Goblin King in order to stop a mortal named The Amazing Krudsky who wants power and is a threat to their pals, Fred, Velma and Daphne.

movies.title: Scooby-Doo and the Samurai Sword
movies.description: The Mystery Inc. crew travels the globe on a transcontinental treasure hunt to solve a series of ancient riddles. Scooby-Doo and Shaggy are indoctrinated by an unlikely Sword Master.

movies.title: Scooby-Doo! Abracadabra-Doo
movies.description: The gang goes on a trip to check on Velma's younger sister, Madelyn. She's been studying stage magic at the Whirlen Merlin Magic Academy, where apparently there have been sightings of a giant griffin. The gang decides to investigate.

movies.title: Scooby-Doo! Camp Scare
movies.description: Scooby-Doo, Shaggy, Freddy, Daphne and Velma fish for clues to solve the mysteries of The Woodsman, The Fishman and The Banshee of Black Canyon.

movies.title: Scooby-Doo! Music of the Vampire
movies.description: When Daphne becomes the star of a vampire film, the production is thrown into chaos by a real vampire, forcing the Scooby-Doo team to investigate who's behind this monstrous mayhem.

movies.title: Big Top Scooby-Doo!
movies.description: Scooby-Doo and the gang go on vacation to Atlantic City, but they get involved in a mystery at a circus.

movies.title: Scooby-Doo! Haunted Holidays
movies.description: An evil snowman comes to life threatening to shut down as toy store. Scooby and the gang to the rescue

movies.title: Scooby-Doo! Adventures: The Mystery Map
movies.description: Scooby-Doo and the gang find a treasure map in a pizza and set out to find the treasure of Gnarlybeard the Pirate, encountering Gnarlybeard, the Phantom Parrot, a spooky lighthouse keeper, and a suspicious archaeologist along the way.

movies.title: Scoob!
movies.description: Scooby and the gang face their most challenging mystery ever: a plot to unleash the ghost dog Cerberus upon the world. As they race to stop this dogpocalypse, the gang discovers that Scooby has an epic destiny greater than anyone ...

movies.title: Scooby-Doo Live Action
movies.description: After an acrimonious break up, the Mystery Inc. gang are individually brought to an island resort to investigate strange goings on.

movies.title: Scooby-Doo 2: Monsters Unleashed
movies.description: The Mystery Inc. gang must save Coolsville from an attack of their past monsters brought to life by an evil masked figure trying to take down the gang.

movies.title: Scooby-Doo! And Krypto, Too!
movies.description: Follows Scooby-Doo and Mystery Inc. as they are looking into the disappearance of the Justice League.
